            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"acr-qa-automated-code-review-quality-assurance\">ACR-QA \u2014 Automated Code Review &amp; Quality Assurance</h1>\n<h3 id=\"thesis-defense-walkthrough-v380\">Thesis Defense Walkthrough \u00b7 v3.8.0</h3>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">This notebook demonstrates the <strong>full ACR-QA pipeline</strong> end-to-end:</span>\n<ol>\n<li>Load a target repository</li>\n<li>Static analysis (Semgrep + Bandit + Ruff + Gosec)</li>\n<li>Taint tracking (source \u2192 sink data-flow)</li>\n<li>AI triage (LLM-powered false-positive reduction)</li>\n<li>Auto-fix patch generation</li>\n<li>Supply-chain risk + SBOM</li>\n<li>Signed attestation (ECDSA-P256 + Dilithium3)</li>\n<li>Quality gate enforcement</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Zero egress required.</strong> All LLM calls can be routed to local Ollama.</span>\n</blockquote></span>"
