            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h3 id=\"taint-flow-diagram\">Taint Flow Diagram</h3>\n<div class=\"language-tsql codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">SOURCE</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">request</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">args</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"k\">get</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;user_id&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"err\">\u2502</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">HTTP</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">query</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">parameter</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">\u2014</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">attacker</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">controlled</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"err\">\u25bc</span>\n<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">HOP 1</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">user_id</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">\u2500\u2500\u25ba</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">format_query</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nf\">user_id</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"err\">\u2502</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">String</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">interpolation</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">no</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sanitization</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"err\">\u25bc</span>\n<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">HOP 2</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">sql</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"ss\">&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE id={user_id}&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"err\">\u2502</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">Tainted</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">string</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">construction</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"err\">\u25bc</span>\n<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">SINK</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">db</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"k\">execute</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">sql</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"err\">\u2190</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">SQL</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">INJECTION</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">\u2717</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Confidence:</strong> 0.87 \u00b7 <strong>Engine:</strong> TaintAnalyzer v3.6.3</span></span>"
